        <div class="dp-caveat-label">Read this in the same glance</div>
        <p><strong>A forward personal projection is exactly where complacency is most dangerous.</strong> The recommendation above is the channel&rsquo;s tendency, not a promise &mdash; the <a href="#cautions">cautions below</a> are the load-bearing part of this page, not the footnotes.</p>
        <p><strong>The math models a holder who never capitulates.</strong> If deploying a lump and watching it fall would push you to sell and leave, laddering or a hybrid is staying-power insurance &mdash; a small expected cost for steadiness the numbers can&rsquo;t see.</p>
